<p>But it did not speak to the power of communities harnessing their own data, which is the point.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Draft 2</span></p>

  <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Weâ€™re organizing the web in Boise, Idaho, around community data, relevant research, government reports, local journalism and public ideas in a structured way that scales to communities around the world.</span></p>
