<p>Then, how will it benefit these communities?</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Draft 4</p>

  <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Weâ€™re marshalling community data alongside relevant university research, government reports, local journalism and public ideas in Boise, Idaho with an open source web app that communities across the world can use to tell their own data stories.</span></p>
